Wilmington.Woodbrook, Delaware:
Woodbrook is an unincorporated community in New Castle County, Delaware, United States.


== Location ==
The community of Woodbrook is located about 3 miles north of Wilmington, Delaware and is part of unincorporated Brandywine Hundred of New Castle County. The community surrounds the DuPont Championship Course of the DuPont Country Club, and has entrances from Rockland Road, Blackgates Road, and Sharpley Road.
